{
  "_comment": [
    "RepeatSolveLoot.json — weighted loot table for repeat quest solves (2nd, 3rd, etc.)",
    "",
    "HOW IT WORKS:",
    "  All enabled groups are flattened into a single pool. Each group has a Weight.",
    "  All items within a group are equally likely — the group Weight determines how",
    "  often ANY item from that group is picked relative to other groups.",
    "",
    "  Effective drop chance for one item =",
    "    GroupWeight / TotalPoolWeight / ItemsInGroup",
    "",
    "  Example with two groups:",
    "    Common (Weight: 1000, 10 items)  → each item: 1000/11000/10 = ~0.9% chance",
    "    Rare   (Weight: 100,   2 items)  → each item:  100/11000/2  = ~0.45% chance",
    "",
    "WEIGHT TIERS (suggested):",
    "  Common:      1000",
    "  Uncommon:     100",
    "  Rare:          10",
    "  Ultra-Rare:     1",
    "",
    "DISABLING A GROUP:",
    "  Set its Weight to 0. Items are still listed for reference.",
    "",
    "DISABLING A SINGLE ITEM:",
    "  Remove it from the Wcids list, or move it to a group with Weight 0.",
    "",
    "PER-QUEST OVERRIDES:",
    "  Add an entry to QuestOverrides keyed by the quest's internal name.",
    "  When that quest triggers a repeat-solve drop, its groups are used",
    "  INSTEAD OF the global groups above. Same Weight/Wcids structure.",
    "  Set QuestOverrides to {} to use only the global table for all quests."
  ],

